          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Reference Geometry</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is a sketch-element that is copied onto the Base-Part in the &apos;active&apos; Mechanism-Editor from a Part in a different Mechanism-Editor. If you edit or move the source sketch-element, the Reference Geometry in the active Mechanism-Editor also updates to the new size or position.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Reference-Geometry</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> may be moving.</text></para>
